//annotations in playwright:

1.test.describe(); - Describe is useful, especially when we want to group multiple test caeses togetaer at the one place.
2.test.only();:- Test.only is going to help you to run only particular test case.
3.test.skip();- test.skip is going to help you to skip particular test case.(it will be used in both describe and test block).
4.test.fixme();- test.fixme is going to help you to mark the particular test case as a fixme. (It will be used in both describe and test block).
5.test.fail();- test.fail is going to help you to mark the test case as a failing test case.(It will be used in both describe and test block).
6.test.slow();- test.slow is going to help you to mark the test case as a slow test case.(It will be used in both describe and test block).
7.test.setTimeout();- test.setTimeout is going to help you to set the timeout for a particular test case.(It will be used in both describe and test block).